OL,3,CBirmingham City Council budget cuts to
OL,4,Cbe 'largest' in local authority history
OL,6,FThe 'largest' budget cut in local
OL,7,Fauthority history has been announced by
OL,9,FThe damning indictment was made by the
OL,10,Fthink tank, The Audit Reform Lab, as
OL,11,Fthe authority put some flesh on the
OL,12,Fbones of plans to save #300m over two
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FCouncil leader, John Cotton said: "The
OL,16,Fproposals that we'll be publishing
OL,17,Ftoday set out cuts of #150 million and
OL,18,Falso a proposal to take advantage of
OL,19,Fthe powers we've been given by the
OL,20,Fgovernment to bring in a 10% council
OL,21,Ftax increase this year and next.
