OL,6,F"This is a really, really difficult
OL,7,Fbudget and it's a really difficult set
OL,8,Fof choices that we've had to make.
OL,10,F"We are like every other council up
OL,11,Fand down the land dealing with the
OL,12,Fconsequences of a massive crisis in
OL,13,Flocal government funding.
OL,15,F"We've lost #1 billion from since
OL,16,F2010, and that's made this challenge
OL,17,Feven more difficult for us to meet.
