OL,6,FCllr Cotton continued: "We're taking
OL,7,Fsteps to ensure we're protecting our
OL,8,Fwellbeing centres that serve some of
OL,9,Fthe most deprived communities in the
OL,10,Fcity.
OL,12,F"We also were putting in place a very
OL,13,Fgenerous council tax support scheme,
OL,14,Fso a quarter of households in the city
OL,15,Fwill be receiving some form of cancer
OL,16,Ftax support, help with their bills and
OL,17,Findeed 75,000 households won't be
OL,18,Fpaying anything at all."
