OL,3,CBirmingham City Council budget cuts to
OL,4,Cbe 'largest' in local authority history
OL,6,F"For an administration that had
OL,7,Fpromised to be open and transparent,
OL,8,FthisJis sadly exactly the kind of
OL,9,Fbehaviour we've come to expect from
OL,10,FLabour in Birmingham `Jsymbolically
OL,11,Funderscored by the constant refusal to
OL,12,Fpublish the draft budget and the
OL,13,Fletters they have sent saying they are
OL,14,Fnot going to set a balanced budget
OL,15,Fwithout selling the city's assets.
OL,17,F"The Labour group has been discussing
OL,18,Ftheir plan to gut the city's services
OL,19,Ffor a yearJand yet have left it until
OL,20,Fthe last two weeks to tell Brummies of
OL,21,Ftheir plan."
