OL,3,CBirmingham City Council budget cuts to
OL,4,Cbe 'largest' in local authority history
OL,6,F"The impact of Labour's double whammy
OL,7,Fof reduced services and significantly
OL,8,FincreasedJcouncil tax ` 21% over 2
OL,9,Fyears ` will be particularly painful
OL,10,Ffor residents and businesses in
OL,11,FBirmingham.
OL,13,F"After promising a golden decade, this
OL,14,Fbudget reveals Labour's true legacy
OL,15,FforJBirmingham; fewer services, higher
OL,16,Ftaxes, and more debt. Labour's plans
OL,17,Famount to sellingJyour car to pay the
OL,18,Fmortgage, and then taking out an
OL,19,Fexpensive loan to make up the
OL,20,Fshortfall in subsequent months.
